videos.headline: Jake Browning connects with Fuller for big gain
videos.description: On 3rd and 21, Jake Browning heaves a pass over the middle to Aaron Fuller for a 46-yard gain.

videos.headline: Huskies force first turnover of game
videos.description: JoJo McIntosh forces Oregon RB Kani Benoit to fumble on a big hit late in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Washington's Pettis breaks history on punt return TD
videos.description: Dante Pettis takes the punt all the way to the house for a 64-yard return and breaks the all-time FBS punt return touchdown record, with nine in his career.

videos.headline: Washington's Gaskin fakes out the defense on TD
videos.description: Myles Gaskins takes the sweep to the outside and fools the defense on a 34-yard touchdown run in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Ducks force Browning's 1st INT
videos.description: Jake Browning tries forcing a pass down the sidelines to Dante Pettis but is intercepted by Brady Breeze late in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Jake Browning airs it out for long TD
videos.description: Jake Browning lofts a ball over the middle to Dante Pettis for a 47-yard touchdown early in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Gaskin jukes out Duck defenders
videos.description: Myles Gaskin displays a few cut moves before being taken down following a 24-yard gain.

videos.headline: Coleman appears to be down but was not and scores TD
videos.description: After nearly being taken down on the play, Lavon Coleman breaks out for a 31-yard touchdown on the screen pass from Jake Browning.

videos.headline: Washington's Ahmed breaks free for long TD
videos.description: Salvon Ahmed takes the sweep and cuts to the outside for a 58-yard rushing touchdown in the third quarter.
